[SN]TITLE[SN]
Tesla offers peek into battery factory

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Electric car manufacturer Tesla is building a new battery production facility.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
27 July 2016 Last updated at 09:37 BST
Known as the Gigafactory, the 3,000 acre manufacturing plant has already begun production, but will not be in full swing until around 2020.
The BBC's Dave Lee was invited inside to see the factory in operation.
